Denise Foyil
 Denise Schroetter Foyil,60, Of Jacksonville, Died Dec. 23,2006 at home. No services are planned. She was preceded in death by her parents.
 Surviving are her husband, James Foyil, a son Richard Wrenn, a daughter Jana Wrenn and two stepchildren Matt Galeano and Emily Foyil.

Im very upset she died, she was been living with cervical cancer for the past nine months. It hurt to remember her but I know she's in a better place now.

Denise Foyil I hope you Rest In Peace.
